      "title": "Immigration & Emigration Dept. expands one-day passport service",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Issuance of passports under the one-day service will commence at regional offices in Matara, Vavuniya and Kandy with effect from tomorrow (July 04), the Department of Immigration and Emigration says.",
        "Only 100 applicants per day with prior appointments will be issued their passports, the department said further."
      ],
